  <name>iGNUit Flashcard Trainer</name>

  <summary>Learn using electronic flashcards</summary>

  <description>
    <p>Ignuit is a memorization aid based on the Leitner flashcard system. It
    has a GNOME look and feel, a good selection of quiz options, and supports
    UTF-8. Cards can include embedded audio, images, and mathematical formulae
    (via LaTeX). It can import and export several file formats, including CSV.
    Ignuit can be used for both long-term learning and cramming.
  </p>
  </description>

